Notes: Rose-Hulman earns first win over Franklin in eight attempts.
Jessica Farmer ties school's career record with 100 three-point field goals.
Carrie Wiley (17) and Kiley Wallace (13) establish career-highs for points.
Game.Officials: Lucy Nalin,  Wayne Hopson,  Wayne Patterson
